===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Originally {{och-l|𣶒}} in oracle bone script; {{liushu|p}} of a basin with water. Bronze inscriptions added vertical strokes resembling riverbanks around the character, and the semantic component {{zh-l|*氵}}. Compare the Egyptian hieroglyph {{m|egy|𓈙}} and its variant forms.

